1. Multiple Classes

HTML :
<button class="btn primary login">

CSS :
.btn.primary.login

Playwright
e.g. -> await page.locator(".btn.primary.login").click();

2. Partial Attribute Match

Starts With
input[id^='user']

Ends With
input[id$='name']

Contains
input[id*='user']

Playwright
e.g. -> await page.locator("input[id*='user']").fill("Admin");
